description:
“YOU'RE NO ROCK N' ROLL FUN”

The Li'l Depressed Boy takes a trip with his dream girl to the local thrift store, where he is thrust both into dead people's clothes and a forthcoming birthday party. Can he find the perfect gift in time? Guest-starring Los Angeles indie songstresses The Like!
name: You`re No Rock `n Roll Fun

description: The Autobots have been beaten down, backed into a corner, and harried into making a huge mistake. But the biggest blow has yet to fall, as Prime sets out to face Megatron one-on-one in the final chapter of REVENGE OF THE DECEPTICONS. Nobody dies... but somebody's gonna wish they had.
name: Revenge of the Decepticons Part 5: The Demolished Man

description: It's all out war in Philadelphia, as Optimus Prime and the rest of the Autobots roll out to stop Starscream and his forces from killing Sam Witwicky! The biggest, most explosive battle in Transformers history begins here! The fate of the universe rests on the outcome and the action of this summer's hottest movie heats up right here!
name: Part 3 of 4

volume.name: Transformers: Dark of the Moon Movie Prequel: Rising Storm

description: Ethan Shade was one of the most inept, third-string supervillains on Earth. But now he may be the last supervillain on Earth. During a month long war, the world's superheroes banded together and wiped out the villains with the exception of Shade. He planned to take down one last bank, but the robbery doesn't quite go as planned, and at the end, Shade had accidentally murdered a popular local superhero. As he races for his life, and accidentally compounds his crimes over and over again, Shade realizes that he's at the centre of a web of deception orchestrated by the world's smartest evil genius, and must try to turn things around for himself before it's too late.

name: Die Burgruine
Auf der Richtigen Spur?
Die Wehrwolfe

description: Last Issue

Debuting a one-shot sequel to the popular Thrillkiller miniseries by the team of writer Howard Chaykin and artist Dan Brereton. Batgirl Barbara Gordon, still reeling from Dick Grayson's fate, has teamed up with renegade police detective Bruce Wayne, now known as Batman. But when the Joker returns to become the new crimelord of Gotham City, will Barbara's desire for revenge mean the end of the Dynamic Duo?

A prestige release which is the sequel to Thrillkiller.
name: Thrillkiller '62

description: Captain America's Day One! He's got the strength. He's got the training. But has he got what it takes? A ragtag Special Forces unit takes Captain America on his first mission of World War II. Their orders? Don't get him killed! But when the low-profile assignment draws the attention of Baron Strucker, the future Red Skull and half the Nazi army, it'll be a crash course in super heroics for Marvel's first Avenger!

The touching robot romance comes to a thrilling conclusion as Travis and his maker continue their pursuit of Odette, and Grace proceeds to wreak havoc in order to express her own feelings. But what of Odette's feelings for Asao? Now that he's preparing to graduate, will Odette finally understand what it means to "like" a special someone?
name: Vol. 6

description: Just as Mitsuya gets sick with a nasty cold, Arisaka and Ageha decide to do something about his chilly relationship with Tsuyu. Just what happened between the two V.B. Rose regulars when they were young? When Mitsuya finds out about Tsuyu's arranged marriage meeting he will stop at nothing to prevent the lost love of his life from falling into the hands of another man. Even if he has to put Arisaka in a kimono!
name: Vol. 12

description: Slowly but surely, the world is being painted in new, bright colors by Rakan and his companions. But wait…what happens when the party stumbles upon a graveyard for criminals, complete with the ghost of a woman out for revenge?! It looks like Rakan is about to find himself stuck in a real horror story!
name: The Graveyard of Bells

description: A dramatic standoff between mayor John Bacchus and Team Yuki results in Ninth making the ultimate sacrifice, leaving Yuki with the two diary holders he wants least to kill--his girlfriend Yuno and the benevolent caretaker Eighth. Suddenly, the game gets turned on its head when Yuki's ally Aru Akise learns that he was nothing more than a pawn created by Deus to observe the game...until he is granted a greater power than any remaining player possesses!
name: Vol. 10

description: A blow on the head forces Keidai to relive the final days of Pompeii. The dark events in the past continue to haunt him, but he may at last be able to come to terms with the choices Sirix made on that fateful day, and change how the tragedy unfolded beneath the swirling column of volcanic ash. But Keidai and Sirix both will have to find forgiveness if he ever hopes to move forward and accept his feelings for Mii!
name: Vol. 9

description:
What should have been an easy caper for Ratman goes south when a mysterious hero claiming to be from a secret, elite section of the Hero Association--called "Sector S"-- appears. Unable even to scratch this new hero, Shuto is mercilessly beaten down, and the drubbing was enough to ruin his confidence in himself as Ratman. Will Shuto decide to quit Jackal? What’s a would-be super hero to do?

Chapter Titles

  • Episode 15: Magazine Debut!? Though Very Happy, I Amm Shameful.
  • Episode 16: Threat of "S"
  • Episode 17: Light and Shadow
  • Episode 18: Quit the Hero
  • Episode 19: Shuto Katsuragi Raising Project
  • Episode EX: Tiny Tot Riot
name: Vol. 4

description: “Hachikuma” aims to deepen the Inui clan’s suspicion of Renkaku, but Renkaku is on to him...or is he just on to the fact that his beloved Eiji has a crush on Hachikuma? Meanwhile, Beni struggles with her growing feelings for young Kagetora--but how will their feelings now affect things further down the time stream? And Big Kagetora is in for a huge surprise the next time he goes back to the future--he finds Beni, sort of, plus an old friend he never dreamed he'd see again!
name: Vol. 7

description: In the continuing adventures at Neko Ramen, Taisho adopts more cats, puppies, prairie dogs and even anteaters! Can all the species cohabitate in his crazy ramen shop? And when Taisho attempts to go eco-friendly, will Tanaka-san be able to stomach it? And what will Tanaka-san do when Taisho discovers ramen fencing?!
name: We're Going Green!  Kind of...

description: It’s her 3rd year of junior high, and Kanoko has to change schools once again! Yet, Kanoko continues to be the perfect “objective observer”. Conflicts between a tomboy and cutesy girl, rivalry between a narcissist and risk-avoider and a delusional girl who escapes into a fantasy world are new additions to Lady Kanoko’s secret notebook. Meanwhile, Kanoko and Haru go to watch a movie shoot where Kanoko tries to solve a series of mysterious accidents involving some of the hottest young actors.
name: Vol. 2

volume.name: The Secret Notes of Lady Kanoko: Warau Kanoko Sama

name: Uberrascht!

description: It's a battle of wits when the Martian Manhunter challenges Batman to penetrate his baffling array of shape-shifting disguises. But when the game goes awry, can even the two heroes defeat the most unexpected menace of all?
name: Now You See Me...

volume.name: The All-New Batman: The Brave and the Bold

description: Set in the Mississippi Delta of the 1920s, this is a classic story of racial injustice, murder, revenge, and music, all told through the clever re-telling of a timeless fairy tale. B.B.'s life seemed simple. But his simple life comes crashing down when the LPs decide to take his land by any means possible. When all is lost, B.B. lashes out, setting into motion acts of revenge that only a big bad wolf could unleash.
name: HC
Der Beweis
Keine Beweise
Drudius Kennt Keine Gnade

description: In 'East Meets West', Betty and Veronica battle in the Wild West to keep the railroad tracks free and clear of the dastardly Rogue Reggie and his gang of train robbers. Before he strikes again, Sheriff Moose must devise a plan to stop the gang for good! Then, in 'Whale of a Sale,' Betty didn't do financially well at her garage sale, but she certainly makes up for it in valuable time spent with Archie!
name: East Meets West

description: In 'The Ultimate Temptation,' Jughead must decide to save his appetite for an all you can eat spread at Veronica's party or go to work for an agency offering him a job as a food sampler! One choice will make him a hero! Then, in 'Pay-Back Fire,' Reggie tries to get the best of Jughead with his over the top practical jokes, but in the end who is it that gets the last laugh?
name: The Ultimate Temptation

description:
Steve Rogers’ black ops femme fatales go on the hunt for a rogue assassin! Fierce fisticuffs, death-defying duels and good ol’ fashioned espionage ensue as everything comes to a head in the Big Apple where the gals go in guns blazin'…Also a secondary story of Silver Sable by Nicieza and Liefeld.

Reprints story from Heads I Win, Tales You Lose Marvel Comics Presents #53.
name: All the Pretty Monsters

volume.name: Captain America and the Secret Avengers

person_credits.role: writer, artist, penciler, letterer, inker, cover

description:
Acclaimed GREEN LANTERN writer Geoff Johns selects and provides commentary on his favorite tales of the Emerald Guardian, originally printed in GREEN LANTERN #7, 40, 59, 162, 173, 177, 182, 183 and 188, GREEN LANTERN (Second Series) #51, GREEN LANTERN CORPS QUARTERLY #6 and GREEN LANTERN CORPS ANNUAL #2.

----------

Emerald inspiration

Acclaimed writer Geoff Johns selects and provides commentary on his picks for the most important and influential GREEN LANTERN tales. As one of the chief architects behind the current popularity of Hal Jordan and the Corps - with such major storylines as REBIRTH and the SINESTRO CORPS WAR - Johns explains how these historic tales of characters and concepts changed the Lanterns mythology forever.

Stories by revered writers John Broome and Alan Moore, along with art by comic book legends Gil Kane, Dave Gibbons and many others, make IN BRIGHTEST DAY a collection every fan of Green Lantern should have.

Many of these stories have elements that will play into the much anticipated storyline GREEN LANTERN: THE BLACKEST NIGHT.
name: In Brightest Day: Tales of the Green Lantern Corps

description: The final arc of the GREEN LANTERN run by acclaimed writer Judd Winick (GREEN ARROW, OUTSIDERS) is collected in this new trade paperback! With Jade at his side, Kyle Rayner, Green Lantern of Earth, takes to stars, where he encounters action and intrigue on Oa, home planet of the Guardians of the Universe! Collects GREEN LANTERN #156 and 158-161.
name: Passing The Torch

name: Dalla neve, con furore

name: La maledizione sepolta
Kerak Gibt Nicht Auf!

description: Issue #263
name: La casa nella tempesta

description: The fan-favorite Eisner Award-winning story, originally serialized in The New York Times Magazine, now collected with 40 pages of new material. Meet Marshall. He's been set up on a blind date with someone named Natalie. Divorced, middle-aged, newly unemployed, with next to no prospects, Marshall isn't exactly a catch. After nearly an hour, when he's long since given up hope, Natalie appears - breathless, apologizing profusely that she went to the wrong place. She's too good to be true: attractive, young, intelligent, and she seems to be seriously engaged with what Marshall has to say. There has to be a catch. And, of course, there is. During the extremely long night that follows, Marshall and Natalie are emotionally tested in ways that two people who just met really should not be. A captivating, bittersweet, and hilarious look at the potential for human connection in an increasingly hopeless world, Mister Wonderful more than lives up to its name.
name: Mister Wonderful: A Love Story

description: COBRA CIVIL WAR BEGINS HERE! The Commander is dead! Long live… Cobra Commander?! But the questions is, who will BE the NEXT Cobra Commander?! The role of Commander must be filled—now the most lethal and cunning Cobra operatives will COMPETE TO REIGN SUPREME. The winner—he who kills the most G.I. JOES—will take the reins of COBRA! Bonus: Ninja Force!!!!! Yeah, baby! 30 big pages of story at regular price! This is the place to jump on board and see what everyone’s been talking about!
name: Cobra Civil War Prelude

description: In the latest chapter of this thrilling adaptation of Robert Jordan's Wheel of Time, Egwene and Moiraine discuss more while Rand eavesdrops, hoping not to be caught by the Aes Sedai, and the travelers end the first leg of their journey at the city of Baerlon. Put up at the Stag and Lion, they're allowed a moment to catch their breath, enjoy a hot bath, and a hot meal. With Lan continually reminding them that they can trust no one, will Rand even be able to find peace in sleep? Discover the answer in the Eye of the World!

volume.name: Robert Jordan's Wheel of Time: The Eye of the World
Doom Patrol: Il Dipinto che Divorò Parigi

description:
Hikaru is in the toughest battle of his life when he faces Ko Yong Ha, Korea's top player in the Hokuto Cup tournament. The stakes, however, aren't for personal glory but for something far deeper, something that differentiates a mere game from a way of life. Hikaru knows what this means to him, but will he understand what it means to the new wave of go players and, indeed, the game of go itself?

Final Volume
name: Endgame

description: The Hokuto Cup games are about to begin, and Hikaru gets caught up in some misunderstandings that make it difficult for him to concentrate on go. In the first match between Japan and China he starts out poorly and seems well on the way to a resounding defeat. Only by getting a tight grip on himself can he possibly make a showing, but that's far easier said than done!
name: China vs. Japan

Makoto has a fever, and his closest friends' concern over his sickness may be the very thing that reveals Makoto's secret to his classmates - forcing him to give up his dreams and return home! Then Ito is caught on the grounds of the Narita residence by Makoto's father, and her life is in the hands of fate! Even if Makoto is able to make it to the scene in time, can he stop the very man who taught him to fight from attacking the woman he loves?!
name: Vol. 7

description: Makoto's father is trying to force Akane into an arranged marriage, and to help Makoto, she's willing to do it! But can Makoto allow his sister to marry a man she doesn't even know so that he can get a chance to make a life as an actor? And who is that handsome man who is always there to come to her rescue? Then, Tsugumi invites Ito to the beach, and the whole gang comes along for an adventure so bizarre, it must be a dream. Or is it?
name: Vol. 8

description: One-Shot Re-Presenting the Death of Cobra Commander and announcing the start of the Cobra Civil War.  The issue contains The Death of Cobra Commander from G.I. Joe Cobra #12 as well as 3 classic issues from G.I. Joe featuring Cobra Commander...
name: Cobra Commander Tribute

description:
The conclusion to Utopia, as the X-Men battle against the Dark Avengers and Dark X-Men. Also Scott and Emma come clean about their secrets, learn how the Dark Beast joined the Dark X-men and Gambit goes on a mission to destroy the Omega Machine, and faces his recent past.

Includes material reprinted from Dark X-Men: The Confession #1, Dark X-Men: The Beginning. Dark Avengers/Uncanny X-Men: Exodus #1, and X-Men Legacy Annual #1
